cised, slightly irregular angular letters: Alpha with downward left-sloping cross-bar; quadrate epsilon; quadrate lunate epsilon; quadrate cursive omega, use of supraline for abbreviation marker.\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line4\">Line 1-4\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"20\" atMost=\"25\">20-25\u003C/height>\u003C!-- IGPalermo -->\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462506\">Tauromenium\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2522975\">Taormina\u003C/placeName>\n                            \t\u003Cgeo>37.85358, 15.28851\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0301\" notAfter-custom=\"0500\">4th — 5th century CE (IGPalermo)\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\">No information on discovery is recorded, unpublished until catalogued by Manni Piraino in 1973.\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n             \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n             \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                     \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                 \u003C/xi:fallback>\n             \u003C/xi:include>\n\t  \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     \u003Cxi:fallback>\n\t       \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n\t     \u003C/xi:fallback>\n\t   \u003C/xi:include>\n         \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-26\" who=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa encoded text division, cleaned up the autogenerated text and checked the edition\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-18\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2024-07-30\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised from publications\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-24\" who=\"#ZL\">tagged names and persons\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface/>\u003C!-- \n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001581_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001581.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>ἀνεπαύσα\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">το\u003C/supplied> \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">Θεό\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>δοῦλος\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003CpersName type=\"divine\">\u003Cname>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">Ἰ\u003C/hi>\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ησοῦ\u003C/ex>\u003Cabbr>\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">ς\u003C/hi>\u003C/abbr>\u003C/expan>\u003C/name> \u003Cname>\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Χ\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ριστό\u003C/ex>\u003Cabbr>ς\u003C/abbr>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>νώνες Ἀ\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\">\u003Cdesc>month name\u003C/desc>\u003C/gap>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>ζήσας ἔ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">τη\u003C/supplied> \u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\">\u003Cdesc>number of years\u003C/desc>\u003C/gap>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text after Ferrua\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"2\">\u003Cnote>Manni Piraino: δοῦλ\u003Cunclear>ο\u003C/unclear>ς Ἰ(η)σ(οῦ)\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Ferrua rejects Manni Piraino's reading of line 2, noting that ΙΣ must be resolved in the nominative and that this most likely followed by an abbreviation (probably employing a christogram) for Christos. The missing month in line 3 must be either April or August.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGMusPalermo\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Manni Piraino\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>1973\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>117\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F66S4X3M\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>no.487\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/759ZXHKQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Muscolino\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2011-2012\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>225 G8 fig.9\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GJKY97S8\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
